   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from Datapipeline import Datapipeline\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score, StratifiedKFold\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import recall_score, accuracy_score, precision_score, f1_score\n",
    "\n",
    "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier\n",
    "from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier\n",
    "from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\n",
    "from sklearn.naive_bayes import GaussianNB\n",
    "from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier\n",
    "\n",
    "from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier, StackingClassifier"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "stacking_RF_GNB_KNN_LR = StackingClassifier(\n",
    "    estimators= [\n",
    "        (\"Random Forest\", RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)),\n",
    "        (\"Naive Bayes\", GaussianNB()),\n",
    "        (\"KNN\", KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=5, weights = 'distance'))\n",
    "        ], \n",
    "    final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42)\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "stacking_RF_GNB_LR = StackingClassifier(\n",
    "    estimators= [\n",
    "        (\"Random Forest\", RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)),\n",
    "        (\"Naive Bayes\", GaussianNB())\n",
    "        ], \n",
    "    final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42)\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "stacking_KNN_GNB_LR = StackingClassifier(\n",
    "    estimators= [\n",
    "        (\"Naive Bayes\", GaussianNB()),\n",
    "        (\"KNN\", KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=5, weights = 'distance'))  \n",
    "        ], \n",
    "    final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42)\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "stacking_RF_KNN_LR = StackingClassifier(\n",
    "    estimators= [\n",
    "        (\"Random Forest\", RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)),\n",
    "        (\"KNN\", KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=5, weights = 'distance'))\n",
    "        ], \n",
    "    final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42)\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "models = [\n",
    "    DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=42), \n",
    "    RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42), \n",
    "    LogisticRegression(random_state=42, max_iter=3000, penalty=\"l2\", C=0.5), \n",
    "    GaussianNB(), \n",
    "    KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=5, weights = 'distance'), \n",
    "    stacking_RF_GNB_KNN_LR, \n",
    "    stacking_RF_GNB_LR, \n",
    "    stacking_KNN_GNB_LR,\n",
    "    stacking_RF_KNN_LR\n",
    "]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df = pd.read_csv('../train.csv')\n",
    "labels = df['Churn']\n",
    "df = df.drop('Churn', axis='columns')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "pl = Datapipeline()\n",
    "skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=10, shuffle=True, random_state=42)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=42)\n",
      "RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)\n",
      "LogisticRegression(C=0.5, max_iter=3000, random_state=42)\n",
      "GaussianNB()\n",
      "KNeighborsClassifier(weights='distance')\n",
      "StackingClassifier(estimators=[('Random Forest',\n",
      "                                RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)),\n",
      "                               ('Naive Bayes', GaussianNB()),\n",
      "                               ('KNN',\n",
      "                                KNeighborsClassifier(weights='distance'))],\n",
      "                   final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42))\n",
      "StackingClassifier(estimators=[('Random Forest',\n",
      "                                RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)),\n",
      "                               ('Naive Bayes', GaussianNB())],\n",
      "                   final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42))\n",
      "StackingClassifier(estimators=[('Naive Bayes', GaussianNB()),\n",
      "                               ('KNN',\n",
      "                                KNeighborsClassifier(weights='distance'))],\n",
      "                   final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42))\n",
      "StackingClassifier(estimators=[('Random Forest',\n",
      "                                RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)),\n",
      "                               ('KNN',\n",
      "                                KNeighborsClassifier(weights='distance'))],\n",
      "                   final_estimator=LogisticRegression(random_state=42))\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "scores_acc = []\n",
    "scores_pre = []\n",
    "scores_recall = []\n",
    "scores_f1 = []\n",
    "\n",
    "for model in models:\n",
    "    print(model)\n",
    "    pl = Datapipeline()\n",
    "    pl.steps.append(['classifier', model])\n",
    "    acc_score = cross_val_score(pl, df, labels, scoring='accuracy', cv=skf)\n",
    "    scores_acc.append(acc_score)\n",
    "\n",
    "    pre_score = cross_val_score(pl, df, labels, scoring='precision', cv=skf)\n",
    "    scores_pre.append(pre_score)\n",
    "\n",
    "    recall_score = cross_val_score(pl, df, labels, scoring='recall', cv=skf)\n",
    "    scores_recall.append(recall_score)\n",
    "\n",
    "    f1_score = cross_val_score(pl, df, labels, scoring='f1', cv=skf)\n",
    "    scores_f1.append(f1_score)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "model_names = [\n",
    "    'DecisionTreeClassifier', \n",
    "    'RandomForestClassifier', \n",
    "    'LogisticRegression', \n",
    "    'Naive Bayes',\n",
    "    'KNN', \n",
    "    'stacking_RF_GNB_KNN_LR', \n",
    "    'stacking_RF_GNB_LR', \n",
    "    'stacking_KNN_GNB_LR',\n",
    "    'stacking_RF_KNN_LR'\n",
    "]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def box_plot_score(score, score_name, model_names = model_names):\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(8, 4))\n",
    "    plt.boxplot(score)\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('Model', fontsize=5)\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('Score', fontsize=5)\n",
    "    plt.xticks(np.arange(len(model_names))+1, model_names, rotation=45, fontsize=8)\n",
    "    plt.title(score_name, fontsize=5)"
   ]
  },

    "for i in range(len(model_names)):\n",
    "    print(model_names[i])\n",
